    <title>Pyecharts基本使用</title>
    <url>/posts/3ad48e02.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Pyecharts基本使用"><a href="#Pyecharts基本使用" class="headerlink" title="Pyecharts基本使用"></a>Pyecharts基本使用</h1><p>绘制第一个图<br><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from pyecharts.charts import Bar</span><br><span class="line">bar = Bar()</span><br><span class="line">bar.add_xaxis(&quot;Mon&quot;,&quot;Tue&quot;,&quot;Wen&quot;,&quot;Tus&quot;,&quot;Fri&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">bar.add_yaxis(30,10,50,14,31)</span><br><span class="line">bar.render()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><br>上述代码会生成一个文件名为<code>render.html</code>的html文件，可以直接打开<br>如果想直接<code>jupyter notebook</code>里面看到效果，可以把上述代码改为如下<br><div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from pyecharts.charts import Bar</span><br><span class="line">bar = Bar()</span><br><span class="line">bar.add_xaxis(&quot;Mon&quot;,&quot;Tue&quot;,&quot;Wen&quot;,&quot;Tus&quot;,&quot;Fri&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">bar.add_yaxis(30,10,50,14,31)</span><br><span class="line">bar.render_notebook() # 只改了这一行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><br><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="../../../images/pyecharts-1.png"
                      alt="Alt text"
                ></p>
]]></content>
